About this Item

"Selected Poems including the verse play Eli." Jonathan Cape: London, 1968. Signed by author on title page. Marked for her "outstanding lyrical and dramatic writing, which interprets Israel's destiny," Nelly Sachs' 1966 Prize cemented women writers' reputations as global cultural commentators.
